    <!-- Help -->
    <string name="help_title">Help</string>
    <string name="help_section_faq">Frequently asked questions</string>
    <string name="help_faq_collapse">Collapse</string>
    <string name="help_faq_expand">Expand</string>
    <string name="help_section_contact">Contact</string>
    <string name="help_contact_send_email">Send e-mail</string>
    <string name="help_contact_email">hello@codewhiskers.app</string>
    <string name="help_faq1_q">How to create a new event?</string>
    <string name="help_faq1_a">Tap the + button on the bottom bar and fill in the name, date, and description. After creating the event, you can add modules like voting, expenses, or carpool.</string>
    <string name="help_faq2_q">How to invite friends?</string>
    <string name="help_faq2_a">In the event settings, you\'ll find a sharing link. You can copy it or share it directly through any app. Invitees join with one tap.</string>
    <string name="help_faq3_q">How do expenses work?</string>
    <string name="help_faq3_a">In the Expenses module, add an expense and enter the amount. You can choose who paid and how to split it. The app automatically calculates settlements.</string>
    <string name="help_faq4_q">How does voting work?</string>
    <string name="help_faq4_a">In the Voting module, create a poll with options and other participants can vote. Results are shown in real time.</string>
    <string name="help_faq5_q">How to change event settings?</string>
    <string name="help_faq5_a">On the event dashboard, tap Settings. Here you can change the name, description, security, budget, and more.</string>
    <string name="help_faq6_q">How does carpool work?</string>
    <string name="help_faq6_a">In the Carpool module, you can offer seats in your car or join someone else\'s ride. Everyone can see who is driving and how many seats are available.</string>
    <string name="help_faq7_q">How do rooms work?</string>
    <string name="help_faq7_a">In the Rooms module, anyone can create rooms with a set capacity. Tap a room to join it — you can only be in one room at a time. Tap again to leave.</string>
    <string name="help_faq8_q">What is the packing list?</string>
    <string name="help_faq8_a">The packing list is a shared checklist of items needed for the event. Anyone can add items and mark what\'s already covered, so nothing gets forgotten.</string>
    <string name="help_faq9_q">What is the difference between Free and Pro?</string>
    <string name="help_faq9_a">The Free plan allows up to 2 events with max 8 participants and 1 poll. Pro unlocks up to 5 events, 100 participants, unlimited polls, expense export, and removes ads.</string>
    <string name="help_faq10_q">How to secure an event with a PIN?</string>
    <string name="help_faq10_a">In event settings, enable PIN protection and set a code. Anyone who wants to join will need to enter the PIN first.</string>

